title: Chrome Force One with Alyssa Vingan Klein
description:
Put her Marc Jacobs sweater in the rafters, folks! Throwing Fits welcomes Nylon Magazine editorial director Alyssa Vingan Klein to the third timer’s club. Fan favorite and the pod’s cool aunt joints the boys to discuss the disaster that is New York Fashion Week, being close, personal friends with Bella Hadid, navigating the media hellscape in 2020, what to wear and how to act on a first date, and much more. Please enjoy 2 and a half plus hours of uncut gems. The Only Podcast That Matters™ has never been more relentless.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
